SYMBOL DOES NOT WORK AS KEYS IN REACT LISTS. REACT TRYIES TO CONVERT SYMBOL TO STRING AND IT CAUSES AN ERROR.

Example:
const numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5];
const listItems = numbers.map((numbers) =>
  <li key={Symbol()}>{numbers}</li>
);

ReactDOM.render(
  <ul>{listItems}</ul>,
  document.getElementById('root')
);

